              <p class="v2-sel-stat"><span class="v2-sel-stat-num">7–20</span><span class="v2-sel-stat-unit">kW</span><span class="v2-sel-stat-sep">·</span><span class="v2-sel-stat-time">5–7 hrs to full</span></p>
              <p class="v2-sel-desc">Daily and overnight charging for multifamily, workplace, retail, and commercial sites. {l2Products.length} models.</p>
              <span class="v2-sel-cta">
                <span>Explore Level 2</span>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
