                <img class="v2-sel-reflection" src="/images/chargers/tellus/evium-dcfc-120kw.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="v2-sel-body">
              <span class="v2-sel-badge v2-sel-badge--dc">L3 · DC Fast</span>
              <h3 class="v2-sel-title">Level 3</h3>
              <p class="v2-sel-stat"><span class="v2-sel-stat-num">30–300</span><span class="v2-sel-stat-unit">kW</span><span class="v2-sel-stat-sep">·</span><span class="v2-sel-stat-time">15–90 min to 90%</span></p>
              <p class="v2-sel-desc">High-turnover retail, fleet depots, and highway corridors that need fast top-ups. {l3Products.length} models.</p>
              <span class="v2-sel-cta v2-sel-cta--dc">
