      {/* ── Bottom zone ──────────────────────────────────
          Holds the brand morph + a slot for the "alternative
          tier" mini button. In idle / brand states the slot
          collapses to 0fr so brand fills the full width. In
          state-l2 / state-l3 the slot opens to 1fr (with brand
          becoming 2fr next to it), revealing a small card that
          lets the user switch to the OTHER tier without
          scrolling back up to the selector cards. */}
      <div class="v2-bottom-zone" data-bottom-zone>
      <div class="v2-bottom-row">
      <div class="v2-brand-morph" data-morph="brands" data-level-panel="brands" data-lv4-anchor="products-brands">
        <div
          class="v2-brand-morph-header"
          role="button"
          tabindex="0"
          data-brand-trigger
          aria-label="Browse the full catalog by brand"
